    {
      "id": "5e748712-e07e-4e0c-a27a-5051ed319966",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $f : {\\R} \\to {\\R^+}$ une fonction de classe $\\mathcal{C}^2$.\nOn suppose : $\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f''(x)| \\le M$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f : {\\R} \\to {\\R^+}\\)</span> une fonction de classe <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}^2\\)</span>. On suppose : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f&#39;&#39;(x)| \\le M\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6851fea5-223b-4b68-a34a-7028b010ae9b",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que : $\\forall\\ x,y \\in \\R,\\ f(x) + yf'(x) + \\frac {y^2}2M \\ge 0$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x,y \\in \\R,\\ f(x) + yf&#39;(x) + \\frac {y^2}2M \\ge 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "69141b2a-5b1e-40a9-8193-aabf888d099b",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$= f(x+y) + \\frac {y^2}2(M-f''(z))$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(= f(x+y) + \\frac {y^2}2(M-f&#39;&#39;(z))\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a051a4d2-8247-46ec-9b84-5050cf912f54",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En déduire que : $\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f'(x)| \\le \\sqrt{2Mf(x)}$.",
        "html": "<p>En déduire que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f&#39;(x)| \\le \\sqrt{2Mf(x)}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "cfe3e769-8b51-418f-ae9e-42cd5e3b1c58",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\Delta \\le 0$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Delta \\le 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0e15a929-252c-4576-8c33-c551017c8526",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On suppose que : $\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f'(x)| = \\sqrt{2Mf(x)}$.\n    Que pouvez-vous dire de $f$ ?",
        "html": "<p>On suppose que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f&#39;(x)| = \\sqrt{2Mf(x)}\\)</span>. Que pouvez-vous dire de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0914bcff-5ab8-4bb3-bc84-483910d4faea",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sqrt f$ est affine.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sqrt f\\)</span> est affine.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
